The '''Fizz''' was a corrosive acid that plagued [[Woteba]] and the other worlds in the [[Utegetu Nebula/Legends|Utegetu Nebula]], causing those who were exposed to it to corrode and [[Death/Legends|die]]. After analysis of the substance by [[Cilghal]], the [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] determined that the Fizz was an environmental defense system featuring nanotechnology beyond anything of the [[Galactic Federation of Free Alliances|Galactic Alliance]], the [[Killik/Legends|Killik]], and the [[Chiss/Legends|Chiss]]. It would attack anything that appeared to harm the environment of the planets in the Nebula.

The other planets controlled by the Killiks were seeded with the Fizz at the end of the [[Swarm War]], in an attempt to prevent them from rebuilding [[the Colony]]. The Dark Nest used this Fizz to turn [[Unu]] against the Jedi.

